{"tid":450142,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp 今天開始加入「回收」已發訊息功能！","createTime":"2017-10-28T01:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T04:36:53.000Z","uid":28412,"like":164,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc3c219cde15a5d146222feb547bc86a4747a7d","tid":450142,"uid":28412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T01:10:18.000Z","msg":"不時有人在 WhatsApp 因為傳錯訊息到其他人或 Group，繼而出現種種的災難。簡單的例子，是在公司的同事 WhatsApp Group 罵老板，但發錯了訊息給老板看。今後，這問題可能會得到解決！<br />\n<br />\n全球逐步開放中<br />\n<br />\n今天開始，全球多個地區的 WhatsApp 用戶開始逐步收到這功能的啟動（你如果未有，可能要等一會）。然而，這功能必須雙方也是使用最新的 WhatsApp 才可以啟動。如果接收訊息的一方是使用舊版 WhatsApp，此功能將無法使用。當然，如果對方眼明手快，你也無法將發出去的訊息當作沒發過吧？<br />\n<br />\n啟動 Delete for Everyone 條件<br />\n<br />\n- 雙方也用最新版 WhatsApp<br />\n- 發送訊息在 7 分鐘之內<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/091006_30efcff35fbfc38e94ac750de819267c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F091006_30efcff35fbfc38e94ac750de819267c.jpg&h=16788246&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d977c75e09fcbd6487a00e7284ce52ddead125c","tid":450142,"uid":60655,"like":887,"dislike":7,"score":880,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T01:13:36.000Z","msg":"hj2q 賓周都損"},{"pid":"cd00939d42867628ad4631d1836c8466cc1e2817","tid":450142,"uid":51701,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T01:19:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hj2q 賓周都損</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd231781e1b7b3c67202894d345982ffdf29e203","tid":450142,"uid":28786,"like":201,"dislike":3,"score":198,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T01:22:14.000Z","msg":"一個群入面唔係個個會更新，打錯左總有人會睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3340dcc0f02f42e815e90f3fed83362e6e4646","tid":450142,"uid":134179,"like":236,"dislike":37,"score":199,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T01:24:00.000Z","msg":"Telegram一早有啦 扮新野？呃9 d細路仔就得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor